title: Hour 1 – Covino and Rich Guest Host
itunes:title: Hour 1 – Covino and Rich Guest Host
description:
Covino and Rich fill in for Dan Patrick and the crew. They recap Covino’s spoiler on Thursday night regarding his Yankees on the heels of a walk-off grand slam by Josh Donaldson. Where does the walk off grand slam rank? Plus, the guys pose the best feeling in sports question to the audience.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
